<HL>
   Politics &amp; Policy:
   Milken May Get
   Immunity to Talk
   About Junk Bonds
   ----
   By Paul Duke Jr.
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/30/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A4
